&lt;p&gt;Alternatively, the reshape may be done using a &lt;em&gt;pivot spec&lt;/em&gt; that offers finer control (see link below):&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre class=&quot;lang-r s-code-block&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;hljs language-r&quot;&gt;spec &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-operator&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;-&lt;/span&gt; a &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-operator&quot;&gt;%&amp;gt;%&lt;/span&gt;
